#: templates/relay_device_info.html:265
msgid "or bigger"
msgstr "o mayor"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:266
msgid ""
"Pump <b>stop</b> if water level get closer to the sensor <b>blind "
"area</b> defined at sensor linked settings."
msgstr "La bomba <b>se detiene</b> si el nivel de agua se acerca al <b>area ciega</b> del sensor definida en la configuracion del sensor vinculado."

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:267
msgid ""
"Pump <b>stop</b> if the sensor is <b>offline</b> or controller lose "
"internet connection."
msgstr "La bomba <b>se detiene</b> si el sensor esta <b>sin conexion</b> o si el controlador pierde conexion a internet."

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:269
msgid "This is an experimental feature; do not use it without supervision."
msgstr "Esta es una funcion experimental; no la uses sin supervision."

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:270
msgid ""
"Ensure all necessary precautions are taken, as it may not work under your"
" specific conditions."
msgstr "Asegurate de tomar todas las precauciones necesarias, ya que podria no funcionar bajo tus condiciones especificas."

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:271
msgid "Use Advanced Settings"
msgstr "Usar configuracion avanzada"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:271
msgid ""
"to customize the smart mode for factors like water tank size, pump flow, "
"and other variables."
msgstr "para personalizar el modo inteligente segun el tamano del tanque, el caudal de la bomba y otras variables."

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:274
msgid ""
"Carefully read the <b>WiFi Water Level S1</b> sensor installation guide "
"before using this feature. Ensure the sensor inside the water tank is not"
" too close to the water inlet or floating valve and consistently provides"
" accurate water level readings."
msgstr "Lee cuidadosamente la guia de instalacion del sensor <b>WiFi Water Level S1</b> antes de usar esta funcion. Asegura que el sensor dentro del tanque no este demasiado cerca de la entrada de agua o de la valvula flotante y que entregue lecturas de nivel de agua consistentes."

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:276
msgid "Open WiFi Water Level S1 Manual"
msgstr "Abrir manual de WiFi Water Level S1"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:285
msgid "Smart Off"
msgstr "Apagado Inteligente"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:287
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3\">\n"
"                    Enable the <b>smart off</b> conditions: <b>End "
"Level</b>, <b>Blind Area</b>, <b>Not Water Flow</b>, <b>Offline "
"Sensor</b>.<br>\n"
"                    If enabled, the pump will stop when the water level "
"reaches <b>End Level &#37;</b> or <b>Blind Area</b>,\n"
