#: templates/relay_device_info.html:358
msgid "Flow Check:"
msgstr "Verificación de Flujo:"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:359 templates/relay_device_info.html:765
msgid "minutes"
msgstr "minutos"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:360
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3\">\n"
"                    When the pump is <b>ON</b>, it checks every X minutes"
" whether it is providing incoming flow.\n"
"                    If no flow is detected, the pump will <b>stop</b> and"
" attempt to restart after <b>3 hours.</b>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3\">\n"
"                    It is recommended to use a value at least three times"
" the sensor update frequency or higher to ensure proper collection of "
"sensor data.\n"
"                    Additionally, depending on your specific flow speed "
"and water tank capacity, more or less time may be required to move 1 "
"centimeter effectively.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3\">\n"
"                    The maximum value is approximately 10 times the "
"sensor update frequency plus 2 minutes, as the pump controller currently "
"stores only the last 10 sensor updates for this feature.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\">\n"
"                    To disable the <b>Flow Check</b> feature, set the "
"value to <b>zero (0)</b>.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <div class=\"row justify-content-md-center my-3\">\n"
"                    <div class=\"col-md-auto my-2\">\n"
"                        Requires: <span class=\"badge text-bg-danger fw-"
"bold\">Smart Mode</span>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                    <div class=\"col-md-auto my-2\">\n"
"                        Don't Depends On: <span class=\"badge text-bg-"
"primary fw-bold\">Smart Off</span>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3\" >\n"
"                    Cuando el motor de agua está <b>encendido</b>, "
"verifica cada X minutos\n"
"                    si está proporcionando flujo entrante.\n"
"                    Si no se detecta flujo, el motor de agua se "
"<b>detendrá</b> y\n"
"                    tratará de reiniciarse después de <b>3 horas.</b>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3\">\n"
"                    Se recomienda usar un valor al menos tres veces la "
"frecuencia de actualización\n"
"                    del sensor o mayor para garantizar una recopilación "
"adecuada de datos del sensor.\n"
"                    Además, dependiendo de la velocidad específica del "
"flujo y la capacidad del tanque de agua,\n"
"                    se puede requerir más o menos tiempo para mover 1 "
"centímetro de manera efectiva.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3\">\n"
"                    El valor máximo es aproximadamente 10 veces la "
"frecuencia de actualización\n"
"                    del sensor más 2 minutos, ya que el controlador del "
"motor de agua actualmente\n"
"                    almacena solo las últimas 10 actualizaciones del "
"sensor para esta función.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\">\n"
"                    Para desactivar la función <b>Verificación de "
"Flujo</b>, establezca el valor en\n"
"                    <b>cero (0)</b>.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <div class=\"row justify-content-md-center my-3\" >\n"
"                    <div class=\"col-md-auto my-2\">\n"
"                        Requiere: <span class=\"badge text-bg-danger fw-"
"bold\">Modo Inteligente</span>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                    <div class=\"col-md-auto my-2\">\n"
"                        No depende de: <span class=\"badge text-bg-"
"primary fw-bold\">Apagado Inteligente</span>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"                "

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:386
msgid "Blind Distance:"
msgstr "Distancia Ciega:"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:389
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3\">\n"
"                    The pump <b>stop</b> if reach the sensor blind "
"distance.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3 alert alert-danger\" role=\"alert\">"
"\n"
"                    It is important to make all necessary adjustments to "
"avoid exceeding the sensor's blind distance.\n"
"                    Otherwise, the sensor may report random water level "
"measurements, potentially causing\n"
"                    <b>erratic behavior</b> in the automatic pump "
"feature.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"\n"
"                <ul class=\"list-group my-3 mx-3\">\n"
"                    <h6 class=\"ms-4\">\n"
"                        Common Sensor Blind Distances\n"
"                    </h6>\n"
"                    <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action\">"
"\n"
"                        <b>AJ-SR04M: </b> 20 CM\n"
"                    </li>\n"
"                    <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action\">"
"\n"
"                        <b>RCWL-1670: </b> 2 CM\n"
"                    </li>\n"
"                </ul>\n"
"                <div class=\"row justify-content-md-center my-3\">\n"
"                    <div class=\"col-md-auto my-2\">\n"
"                        Requires: <span class=\"badge text-bg-primary fw-"
"bold\">Smart Off</span> and <span class=\"badge text-bg-danger fw-"
"bold\">Smart Mode</span>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                    <div class=\"col-md-auto my-2\">\n"
"                        Don't Depends On: <span class=\"badge text-bg-"
"danger fw-bold\">Smart Mode</span> if <span class=\"badge text-bg-warning"
" fw-bold\">Safe Mode</span> in <b>ON</b>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3\">\n"
"                    El motor de agua <b>se detendrá</b> si alcanza la "
"distancia ciega del sensor.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3 alert alert-danger\" role=\"alert\">"
"\n"
"                    Es importante realizar todos los ajustes necesarios "
"para evitar exceder la distancia ciega del sensor.\n"
"                    De lo contrario, el sensor podría reportar mediciones"
" aleatorias del nivel de agua, lo que podría causar\n"
"                    <b>comportamientos erráticos</b> en la función "
"automática del motor de agua.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"\n"
"                <ul class=\"list-group my-3 mx-3\" >\n"
"                    <h6 class=\"ms-4\" >\n"
"                        Distancias Ciegas Comunes de Sensores\n"
"                    </h6>\n"
"                    <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action\" "
">\n"
"                        <b>AJ-SR04M: </b> 20 CM\n"
"                    </li>\n"
"                    <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action\">"
"\n"
"                        <b>RCWL-1670: </b> 2 CM\n"
"                    </li>\n"
"                </ul>\n"
"                <div class=\"row justify-content-md-center my-3\" >\n"
"                    <div class=\"col-md-auto my-2\">\n"
"                        Requiere: <span class=\"badge text-bg-primary fw-"
"bold\">Apagado Iteligente</span> y <span class=\"badge text-bg-danger fw-"
"bold\">Modo Inteligente</span>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                    <div class=\"col-md-auto my-2\">\n"
"                        No depende de: <span class=\"badge text-bg-danger"
" fw-bold\">Modo Inteligente</span> si <span class=\"badge text-bg-warning"
" fw-bold\">Funcionamiento Seguro</span> está <b>ACTIVADO</b>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"                "

